               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-803" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-803" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-803" type="surname" value="MEREDITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-803" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES MEREDITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a wheelwright On the 21st of January, about half-past four o'clock in the afternoon, I was at a public-house at Cam<lb></lb>bridge-heath—the prisoner was there—a piper came in, and a dance was proposed—I danced also, and the prisoner was my partner—I afterwards sat down, and he went out—I did not miss my watch till the landlord called me out—I felt, and my watch was gone from my fob—the prisoner came in again, and said, "Old <hi rend="italic">chap</hi>, how are you?"—my watch. has never been found.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PHILLIPS</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You had all drank too much, perhaps? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No—the prisoner did not appear the least intoxicated.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-804" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-804" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-804" type="surname" value="FAVELL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-804" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FAVELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I was assisting at the public-house, and saw the prisoner and the prosecutor dancing—I saw the prisoner draw the prose<lb></lb>cutor's watch from his pocket, and go out directly—I do not know what he did with it—he remained out from ten minutes to a quarter of an hour.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> I believe the prisoner had been drinking? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> He had.</p>
